{"tid":2267661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"八人銀礦灣Staycation 引爆三條傳播鏈","createTime":"2020-11-02T08:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T06:10:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8bc0232bed6b934e13bd657be643aa99149f2b","tid":2267661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/WZ3JMJBLSBH3FDBXK5FITPRWTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FWZ3JMJBLSBH3FDBXK5FITPRWTE%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=5eb5fd36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FWZ3JMJBLSBH3FDBXK5FITPRWTE%2F&h=0ac52119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/WZ3JMJBLSBH3FDBXK5FITPRWTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n八人銀礦灣Staycation 引爆三條傳播鏈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AcxMvp9x5WCSDyjxo5h3uTWvIec=/1477x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DI2UDIIIVNGDFIHWX6735B7GZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAcxMvp9x5WCSDyjxo5h3uTWvIec%3D%2F1477x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDI2UDIIIVNGDFIHWX6735B7GZU.jpg&h=1ebcf87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■八人到銀礦灣海景渡假樂園Staycation，兩人中招，當中女患者疑再傳給親友，引爆三條傳播鏈。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】再有酒店Staycation爆疫。一名26歲初步確診女子潛伏期間，與七名朋友到梅窩銀礦灣海景渡假樂園Staycation，其中同行任職有線新聞工程部的26歲男友人，以及曾與該女子用膳的15歲男親友亦初步確診，兩男又分別與約10名朋友打邊爐及打籃球，即該群組最少衍生三條傳播鏈。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：偷渡後長留酒店 被捕扣旺角差館  曾接觸23警 內地妓女確診<br />\n<br />\n張竹君於記者會上指，該26歲女子與家人居大埔圍頭村，她於黃竹坑香葉道15號一間公司任文職，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n密切接觸者數以十計<br />\n<br />\n張指，該女子發病前夕，即10月27日曾與同住圍頭村的15歲男親友用膳及談話。這名親友就讀粉嶺基督教香港信義會心誠中學，他10月29日曾與10多名朋友在聯和墟除口罩打籃球，10月30日返學，放學後與同學用膳。他10月31日與家人拜山，同日出現流鼻水，他得悉26歲女患者初步確診後，到急症室求醫及檢測，結果初步確診。中心建議該校停課14天，並會向全校學生派樣本樽進行檢測。曾一同打籃球的朋友被列密切接觸者，會被送檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：衞生署帶走東方泛達三住客<br />\n<br />\n心誠中學在網頁上載通告，指有中三生確診，現正接受治療。學校今起停課兩日，周三起至14日改以網課形式上課。<br />\n<br />\n至於銀鑛灣Staycation同行的26歲男友人，10月30日出現喉嚨痕，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有線電視外事部證實，這名26歲男子是有線新聞工程部員工，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n計及銀鑛灣「Staycation」、親戚拜山及打籃球、粉嶺「打邊爐」，今次暫。。。。。。。。。。，建議市民即使參與酒店活動，也應盡量只與同住親友一起，避免與陌生人接觸，「唔好太密太多人自然好啲」。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會傳染病顧問委員會聯席主席曾祈殷表示，本。。。。。。。。。。。，因為相關聚會難免有除口罩吃飯等緊密接觸，只要一人染疫，傳播機會很大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kcDNzrWLiViyO0hRyELIV86y0sw=/1865x2793/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/65VZ37JROBHABBVTXQZUPUOUOE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkcDNzrWLiViyO0hRyELIV86y0sw%3D%2F1865x2793%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F65VZ37JROBHABBVTXQZUPUOUOE.gif&h=db915b06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20d48e0afbc2b1c5b71a8e134e3002a33c75c123","tid":2267661,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icwkCD1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicwkCD1.jpg&h=58bfb66d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552c9c64407dd9754f81fe61aceea94d0fcf2897","tid":2267661,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"啲八婆港女真係害人不淺<br />\n咁撚鍾意開房玩群交<br />\n<br />\n去下燒烤場唔撚得既<br />\n下下室內扑野唔爆發病毒就假"},{"pid":"aba4c9636bc0c93b8fc1bb686efe991e58090cdc","tid":2267661,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"銀礦灣酒店真係應該告蘋果<br />\n<br />\n一開始就講係銀礦灣酒店<br />\n<br />\n到依家都用銀礦灣酒店幅圖<br />\n<br />\n蘋果係咪比支那人做篇輯？"},{"pid":"f436461ff23bfcf4a04dc5e15d11bb6e6214e81c","tid":2267661,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"淫P群組"},{"pid":"cb7c69b8b378317494ee07f91526b08d79ca947d","tid":2267661,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"叫雞群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}